      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Key model input parameters identified and nominal values documented at Gradation 1 for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity, density, and hemolysis model constants were taken from published sources and documented in the simulation record. Sensitivity analysis was not performed; this is within scope for MRL 2 Gradation 1."
    },
    {
