      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Correspondence between simulation input parameters and experimental conditions documented at Gradation 1 for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles and rotational speed in the CFD model were matched to experimentally measured values. Formal equivalency mapping protocol was not applied; consistent with MRL 2 Gradation 1 requirements."
